        "title": "Rising Action - Crisis 4",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Part 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The lessons learned and fallout resulting from Crisis 3 may not seem too severe. It may even appear as though things are beginning to look up a little for the Protagonist. However, they quickly slide into Crisis 4, which leads them directly into the story's Climax."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Display how the Rising Action to this point is changing the Protagonist (e.g. perhaps they are not quite as set in their old ways and are willing to tone down their flaws)."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Allow this Crisis to offer a glimmer of hope – each Crisis should produce a slight dip in tension to prevent an exhausting rise in tension."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Then, shred the glimmer of hope and drive the Protagonist into Crisis 4 and to the Climax."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Consider any subplot(s)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Example:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "While trying to hide from the human, the squirrel sneaks around the house, lost and trying to find its way to safety. The human, meanwhile, is running through the house trying to find the squirrel, getting more and more upset. The squirrel finally makes its way through the house and finds the back door. It only needs to make it across the living room and through the kitchen. It begins to run across the open space of the living room when, too late, it sees a cat in the corner."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Part 1 makes up approximately the first 65% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Crisis 4 should occur around approximately the 45% mark of the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
