      {
        "id": 4,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 5,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Rising Action - Crisis 2",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Middle of Part 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The fallout from Crisis 1 leads directly into Crisis 2. Things continue to worsen for the Protagonist as they move into the story, and the Rising Action continues. Troubles begin to pile up. "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Demonstrate how the fallout from the actions in the previous beat impact the Protagonist, including how it affects their character arc."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show what lesson they learned, if any, and how they try to recover from the previous Crisis."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Continue to include bits of exposition and backstory to fill in the blanks that occurred before Crisis 1. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Remember to consider any subplot(s) and how these scenes further the Protagonist's transformation. How are the Protagonist's reactions connected to their past experiences and inner conflicts?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Example:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Seeing the backdoor left open once again, the squirrel sneaks back into the house, watching for any sign of the human. It runs in with the coast clear, grabs a few peanuts, and brings them back to the nest. It returns for more and pauses to nibble a peanut in the kitchen, where it is suddenly cornered by the family dog. The dog barks furiously and chases the squirrel deeper into the house where it can get safely out of reach."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Part 1 makes up approximately the first 65% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Crisis 2 should occur around approximately the 15% mark of the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
